  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "fac = Sqrt[M^(-1)]*Sqrt[Pi]*Exp[X^2/(2*\\[Sigma]x^2)]\r\nfac2 = Exp[a^2/(4*M)]\r\ncos1 = Cos[d+(-2*a*c-I*2*b*c)/(4M)]\r\ncos2 = Cos[e+(-2*a*b-I*b^2-I*c^2)/(4M)]\r\nges = fac*fac2*cos1*cos2",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
