   "value": "GaussianIntegrate =\r\n Integrate[\r\n   F,\r\n   {q1,-Infinity,Infinity},\r\n   {q2,-Infinity,Infinity},\r\n   GenerateConditions -> False,\r\n   Assumptions -> {\r\n      \\[Sigma]q>0,\r\n      \\[Sigma]x>0,\r\n      \\[Sigma]p>0,\r\n      \\[HBar]>0,\r\n      m>0,\r\n      t1>0,\r\n      t2>0,\r\n      q>0\r\n   }\r\n ]",
